column12: Precursor contains: Diphtheria toxin fragment A; Diphtheria toxin fragment B.  Sequence numbering given by authors is for the mature Diphtheria Toxin Fragment B which constitutes residues 219-560 in the precursor.  The diphtheria toxin is produced by Corynephage omega taxon id 10714.

Precursor contains: Diphtheria toxin fragment A; Diphtheria toxin fragment B.  Sequence numbering given by authors is for the mature Diphtheria Toxin Fragment B which constitutes residues 219-560 in the precursor.  The diphtheria toxin is produced by Corynephage omega taxon id 10714.
The epitope sequence is from the reference cited: Greenfield et al. (1983) Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A. 80: 6853-6857 [PMID: 6316330]. The epitope was deduced.
